9-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Personality</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Personality Traits</h2></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Kind</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Faithful</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Loyal</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">L = Loyal</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">F = Faithful</span></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-text h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H19a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v18a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H6.5a1 1 0 0 1 0-5H20\"></path><path d=\"M8 11h8\"></path><path d=\"M8 7h6\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Spiritual</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Spiritual Significance</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-slate-800 leading-7\">The name Logan is a reminder of the kindness and compassion found in those who bear it, as well as their unwavering loyalty and faithfulness to their loved ones.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Cultural Context</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Cultural Significance</h2></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\">Logan is a name that has existed in various cultures throughout history. In Scotland, Logan is believed to be a personal name and a place name, derived from the Old Gaelic word &quot;logainm&quot; meaning &#x27;hollow&#x27;. In America, Logan has been popularized by several notable figures, including early American frontiersman and Army officer, Logan Marshall Green, an American actor, and Logan Paul, an American social media influencer.</div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\">The spiritual significance of the name Logan is derived from its Hebrew origins, which suggest the idea of sweetness, gentleness, and the notion of being small but significant in the eyes of God. In the Christian faith, the name Logan reminds us of the importance of humility and the value of each individual child of God. The name Hagar in the Old Testament of the Bible is also a symbol of faithfulness and perseverance, which can be a spiritual reminder for those named Logan. Ultimately, the name Logan is a reminder of the gentle love and care of God for His children, and the importance of humility and faithfulness in our daily lives.</div></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Historical Usage</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Historical References</h2></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">Saint Logan, also known as Saint Logan of Cornwall, was a 5th-6th century Irish monk and bishop. He is said to have founded a monastery at Lanner in Cornwall, England, and is the patron saint of that region. The name Logan may have been a corruption of the Irish word &#x27;olcain&#x27; meaning &#x27;handsome&#x27;.</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">5th-6th century</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">Logan, a 17th-century Scottish clansman and hero, is best known for his role in the Battle of Glenfinnan in 1689. He was a member of the Clan MacLeod and is said to have successfully led his clan against the forces of the deposed King James VII. The name Logan may have originated from the Gaelic word &#x27;lagan&#x27;, meaning &#x27;hollow one&#x27;.</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">17th century</p></div></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Spiritual</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Spiritual Symbolism</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-slate-800 leading-7\">Logan, derived from the Old Celtic word &quot;lagann,&quot; means &quot;hollow&quot; or &quot;little hollow one.&quot; In Christianity, this name symbolizes the emptying of oneself in service to God or the gentle and hidden strength of the faithful.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Modern Usage</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Modern Usage</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\">Logan is a modern name that has gained significant popularity due to its association with the popular character, Wolverine, from Marvel Comics. Wolverine is a renowned superhero known for his retractable bone claws and rapid regenerative ability. The character has been the focus of numerous X-Men films, with the most recent being &#x27;Logan&#x27; (2017), where the titular character is portrayed by Hugh Jackman. Additionally, Logan&#x27;s name is frequently used in video games, both in relation to Wolverine and as an independent name. The use of the name Logan extends beyond comic books and films, as it is a common given name in many English-speaking countries.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Popularity</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Popularity by Region</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\"><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Poland</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->64</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">France</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->54</span></div></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Famous People</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Famous People and Real-World Usage</h2></div></div><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500 mb-3\">Historical Figures &amp; Cultural References</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">Logan Paul</span><span class=\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">Logan Lerman</span></div></section><section class=\"nv-card-solid\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-languages h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m5 8 6 6\"></path><path d=\"m4 14 6-6 2-3\"></path><path d=\"M2 5h12\"></path><path d=\"M7 2h1\"></path><path d=\"m22 22-5-10-5 10\"></path><path d=\"M14 18h6\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Translations</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Name Translations</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500\">Additional language translations available for this name.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"nv-card-solid p-4\"><div class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\"><span>🇺🇸</span><span>English</span></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Logan</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">Little hollow or small valley</p></div><div class=\"nv-card-solid p-4\"><div class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\"><span>🇮🇱</span><span>Hebrew</span></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">לוגן</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">נער או ילד קטן, שמח או משמח</p></div><div class=\"nv-card-solid p-4\"><div class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\"><span>🇬🇷</span><span>Greek</span></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Λογαν</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">Λογος, λογικος, νοημοσύνη</p></div><div class=\"nv-card-solid p-4\"><div class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\"><span>🇮🇹</span><span>Latin</span></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Logan</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">Little hollow, small valley</p></div></div></section></div><section class=\"nv-card-solid\" aria-labelledby=\"similar-names-heading\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></div><div><h2 id=\"similar-names-heading\" class=\"text-x