 but significant in the eyes of God. In the Christian faith, the name Logan reminds us of the importance of humility and the value of each individual child of God. The name Hagar in the Old Testament of the Bible is also a symbol of faithfulness and perseverance, which can be a spiritual reminder for those named Logan. Ultimately, the name Logan is a reminder of the gentle love and care of God for His children, and the importance of humility and faithfulness in our daily lives.\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",false,false]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"60:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L70\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"my-6\\\",\\\"minHeight\\\":\\\"90px\\\",\\\"instanceId\\\":\\\"name-detail-mid\\\"}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"61:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"nv-card\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L1a\\\",null,{\\\"ref\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"iconNode\\\":\\\"$57:props:children:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:iconNode\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"lucide-clock h-5 w-5\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Historical Usage\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-semibold\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Historical References\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\\\",\\\"children\\\"