 modern name that has gained significant popularity due to its association with the popular character, Wolverine, from Marvel Comics. Wolverine is a renowned superhero known for his retractable bone claws and rapid regenerative ability. The character has been the focus of numerous X-Men films, with the most recent being 'Logan' (2017), where the titular character is portrayed by Hugh Jackman. Additionally, Logan's name is frequently used in video games, both in relation to Wolverine and as an independent name. The use of the name Logan extends beyond comic books and films, as it is a common given name in many English-speaking countries.\"}]]}]\n64:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"nv-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1a\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$63:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:children:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-trending-up h-5 w-5\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\",\"children\":\"Popularity\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Popularity by Region\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"Poland\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-slate-600\",\"children\":[\"Score: \",64]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-mediu